          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，李文忠。圣上拜徐达为帅，齐集我等，不知哪路军情。\n唗，马来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李文忠下。胡大海上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡大海",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昔日元朝为将，今保大明家邦。斩将韬略腹内藏，世人闻名胆丧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡大海",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，胡大海。圣上拜徐达为帅，齐集我等，不知哪路军情。\n唗，马来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡大海下。常遇春上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "常遇春",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "铁盔铁甲铁驼龙，跨下乌骓快似风。大喝一声如雷震，手执钢鞭打孽龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "常遇春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，常遇春。圣上拜徐达为帅，齐集我等，不知哪路军情。\n唗，马来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（常遇春上。郭英、李文忠、胡大海、常遇春同上，同下马。〖粉妆台〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭英、李文忠、胡大海、常遇春",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅升帐，两厢伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖大开门〗。众人引徐达同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐达 （双调粉蝶儿） 威镇山江统貔貅，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "威镇山江扫狼烟。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "青霄直上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐达升高坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凛凛威风冠群英，腾腾杀气映斗星。莲花帐内施号令，要把狼烟一扫平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅，徐达。奉圣命，统领人马，攻打采石矶，剿除残暴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军、中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传众将进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。\n令出，元帅有令：传众将进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭英、李文忠、胡大海、常遇春",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，报，众将告进。\n元帅在上，末将等参。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位将军少礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭英、李文忠、胡大海、常遇春",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传末将等进帐，有何差遣？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我奉圣命，统领人马，攻打采石矶，剿除残暴。但彼处山高水深，难以得破，\n不知列位将军，有何妙策？"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启元帅：此去采石矶，白茫茫一带大江，必须舟师，方能攻进。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李文忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅传下号令，多备战船，暗藏惯战水军，足可破敌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡大海",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既如此攻取，谅小小矶头，焉有不克之理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "常遇春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仗圣主威福，元帅神机，定然一鼓而下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，全仗列位将军，努力同心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭英、李文忠、胡大海、常遇春",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "末将等，勤劳王事，分所当然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！分列两旁，听我调遣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭英、李文忠、胡大海、常遇春",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "郭英听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你带领三千弓箭手，五十号战船，先抢牛石渚，后破采石矶，听本帅号令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（江儿水） 圣主威福广，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "挥雄师，会合风云旺。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。\n令出，唗，带马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众士卒",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（郭英下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李文忠听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李文忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你带领三千长枪手，五十号战船，先抢牛石渚，后破采石矶，听本帅令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（江儿水） 捧军令似受天符降，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "立勋犹拟画云台上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李文忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。\n令出，唗，带马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众士卒",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李文忠下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胡大海听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡大海",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你带领三千藤牌手，五十号战船，先抢牛石渚，后破采石矶，听我号令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
