    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众人",
        "众士卒",
        "元大将",
        "常遇春",
        "徐达",
        "胡大海",
        "铁木耳"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（元大将上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "元大将",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "令行山岳动，言出鬼神惊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "元大将",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺奉都督将令，把手牛石渚，远远望见，战船无数，想必敌人来也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡大海上，战，杀元大将，下。铁木耳上，众士卒同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "铁木耳",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大将扬威武，雄似山头虎。杀人汤泼雪，斩将如截土。"
        },
        {
          "character": "铁木耳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，铁木耳。大元驾前为臣。奉狼主之命带领人马，镇守采石矶，以防贼人攻\n取。\n唗，巴都鲁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众士卒",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "铁木耳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打道矶头去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众士卒",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。\n已到矶头。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（铁木耳上城，坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "铁木耳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多备滚木擂石，小心防守者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众士卒",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "内唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离大营上战船风狂浪大，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐达上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有本帅为江山戴月披星。\n对大江设将台扎下行营。\n专待看众儿郎各逞其能。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（郭英、众士卒同上，杀，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小郭英年虽幼骁勇非常，\n可算得我朝中驾海金梁。\n扶江山保社稷四海名扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李文忠、众士卒同上，杀，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李文忠生长在宦室豪门，\n他乃是万岁爷御前外甥。\n五凤楼专与他画影图形。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡大海、众士卒同上，杀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡大海",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，看采石矶，山高水深，怎能得破。也罢，船上有桅，桅上有斗，不免将身\n藏在斗内，纵上矶头便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（铁木耳举石打胡大海。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "铁木耳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "招打！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡大海跌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡大海",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡大海下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胡大海生的来性如烈火，\n大江中统舟师破浪冲波。\n被擂石打落水怎生奈何。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（常遇春、众士卒同上，杀，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "常遇春他本是明辅上将，\n在豪梁夺状元定国安邦。\n全凭他保皇朝辟土开疆。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众士卒同上，同杀，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！你看采石矶，这等坚固，何时得破？有了，我想重赏之下，必有勇夫。\n待本帅传下将令。\n五营四哨，大小将官，听者！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众士卒 （内同白） 吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有人破得采石矶，功为第一，先锋大印，付他执掌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐达下。常遇春上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "常遇春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，方才元帅传下将令，有人破得采石矶，功为第一，先锋大印，付他执掌。\n又道是一人拚命，万夫难挡。船上有桅，桅上有斗，待我将身藏在斗内，纵上\n矶头便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（常遇春登城，杀铁木耳，下。众人同上，杀，同下。徐达、众人同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启元帅：采石矶已破。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就此班师复命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大尾声。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
